MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2017-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 17th June, 2017
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 17th June, 2017:-
Shri Radha Mohan Singh relinquished the additional charge of the office of the Minister of
Consumer Affairs, Food and Public Distribution. He will continue to hold the charge of the
office of the Minister of Agriculture and Farmers Welfare; and
(i)
Shri Ramvilas Paswan relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister without Portfolio
and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Consumer Affairs, Food and Public
Distribution.
S.G.P. Verghese)
